Package au.csiro.pathling.fhirpath.parser.generated

Interface FhirPathListener

All Superinterfaces:
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
All Known Implementing Classes:
FhirPathBaseListener
public interface FhirPathListener extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by FhirPathParser.
